Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:08.12,译文,,0,0,0,,我能在2500米外干掉一个精英战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can take down an Elite at 2, 500 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.96,译文,,0,0,0,,但我的步枪对付一群蜜蜂就毫无用处了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But my rifle is useless against a swarm of bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.46,译文,,0,0,0,,就是说我们现在就是蜜蜂\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So we're bees now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.05,译文,,0,0,0,,你倒是想呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.63,译文,,0,0,0,,蜜蜂会群体合作\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Bees work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.76,译文,,0,0,0,,众多的身体 思想统一\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Many bodies. One mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.97,译文,,0,0,0,,一个任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}One mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:28.81,译文,,0,0,0,,渗入飞船 把尖刺捅进去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Infiltrate the ship. Deliver the spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.94,译文,,0,0,0,,舰桥就是神经中枢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The bridge is the nerve center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:36.65,译文,,0,0,0,,外面有保护 但内部没有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's protected on the outside, not on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.98,译文,,0,0,0,,抵抗不了这个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.61,译文,,0,0,0,,我们的情报显示他们的系统\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Our intel indicates that their system
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.07,译文,,0,0,0,,很容易就被腐败\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}is vulnerable to override.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.95,译文,,0,0,0,,这个刺会传播病毒\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This spike delivers a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.91,译文,,0,0,0,,系统全面关闭\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Full system shutdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.99,译文,,0,0,0,,生机全无\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.50,译文,,0,0,0,,就像脑袋中了一枪一样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Like a bullet to the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:57.00,译文,,0,0,0,,有什么想补充的吗 斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you have something you would like to add, Spartan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.34,译文,,0,0,0,,有的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.13,译文,,0,0,0,,我想说这都是扯淡 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'd like to add it's bullshit, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:05.97,译文,,0,0,0,,我们把敌人都清除了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We cleared the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.93,译文,,0,0,0,,那些子弹都不知道是从哪儿冒出来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Those rounds came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:11.81,译文,,0,0,0,,模拟是随机的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The simulation is random.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.44,译文,,0,0,0,,战争也是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:17.98,译文,,0,0,0,,解散\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.16,译文,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Heyl Heyl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.37,译文,,0,0,0,,我就明说了吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let me be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.99,译文,,0,0,0,,我们不是平等的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We are not equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.33,译文,,0,0,0,,我是你导师\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I am your instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.00,译文,,0,0,0,,你是对我有意见吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you have a problem with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.88,译文,,0,0,0,,我对失败有意见\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have a problem with failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.38,译文,,0,0,0,,对士兵不断\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have a problem with soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:40.88,译文,,0,0,0,,重复犯错有意见\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that continue to repeat mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.09,译文,,0,0,0,,不仅危及到他们的任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}jeopardizing not only their mission
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:43.72,译文,,0,0,0,,还有他们战友的性命\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but the lives of their comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.89,译文,,0,0,0,,我战友们都死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}My comrades were all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.55,译文,,0,0,0,,是在针对我吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is it personal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:50.18,译文,,0,0,0,,是因为当时我在致远星而你不在吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is it 'cause I was on Reach and you weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.31,译文,,0,0,0,,一场战斗不代表你就经验丰富了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}One battle doesn't make you a veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.52,译文,,0,0,0,,只代表你运气好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just makes you lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.86,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道入伍可能会有什么结局\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know what I signed up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.20,译文,,0,0,0,,你是在跟我说你想死吗 斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you telling me you want to die, Spartan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.58,译文,,0,0,0,,不是 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.26,译文,,0,0,0,,他们在地球上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They grew leaves like these
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:30.18,译文,,0,0,0,,一个叫斯里兰卡的一个小家庭果园里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}on a small family orchard in a place called Sri Lanka,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.85,译文,,0,0,0,,种这种茶叶\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.27,译文,,0,0,0,,在阳光下晒干\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Dried in the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:38.06,译文,,0,0,0,,然后又父亲背着走出16英里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}then borne on the back of the father 16 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:39.07,注释,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.28\pos(148.4,68.2)}别浪费他们的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:41.82,译文,,0,0,0,,他那棕色的双脚 那片红色的土地\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}His brown feet, that red earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.24,译文,,0,0,0,,在拍卖会上售出\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sold at auctjon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:46.20,译文,,0,0,0,,然后被人扛上肩膀\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}then placed upon shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.95,译文,,0,0,0,,上了船 出了海\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}then upon ships, then upon seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.20,译文,,0,0,0,,包装 购买\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Packaged, purchased,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.50,译文,,0,0,0,,倒入这个易碎的杯子里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and poured into this fragile cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.33,译文,,0,0,0,,只为了入你的唇\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}just for your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.42,译文,,0,0,0,,不该如此费心的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.04,译文,,0,0,0,,是不该\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:04.42,译文,,0,0,0,,这些茶叶实际上在第四层的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}These leaves were actually engineered in a lab
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.59,译文,,0,0,0,,实验室里改造出来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}on Level Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:12.10,译文,,0,0,0,,为什么海军情报局会关心起泡茶的问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And why would the ONI concern itself with making tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.39,译文,,0,0,0,,因为我让的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Because I told them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:20.52,译文,,0,0,0,,重点的 你喝的是茶 品的却是故事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The point is, you drink the tea, but what you taste is the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.61,译文,,0,0,0,,故事很重要 但它们也很微妙\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stories are important, but they're delicate things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.28,译文,,0,0,0,,茶 就像帝国一样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tea, like empires,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:34.58,译文,,0,0,0,,几个世纪的努力都可能因为一点点疏忽而付之东流\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}centuries of work can be undone by the smallest of oversights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.17,译文,,0,0,0,,如果你关心致远星\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If you're concerned about Reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:44.21,译文,,0,0,0,,那故事情节就不会改变\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}then the narrative remains intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.38,译文,,0,0,0,,不到一小时前 一艘飞船侵入了我们的领空\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A ship penetrated our airspace less than an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:50.22,译文,,0,0,0,,我听说驾驶这艘飞船的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm told whoever piloted the vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:54.14,译文,,0,0,0,,对我们的防御系统有所了解\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}showed some familiarity with our defense network.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:09:00.15,译文,,0,0,0,,希望你这不是在怪我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I hope that you're not blaming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:02.56,译文,,0,0,0,,他们降落的地方离我们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They landed less than 15 kilometers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.02,译文,,0,0,0,,这里不到15公里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}from where we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.65,译文,,0,0,0,,派支队伍去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Send a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:13.41,译文,,0,0,0,,我有没有提过 我们一位来自阿莱利亚星的特工\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did I mention that, uh, one of our agents from Aleria
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:16.04,译文,,0,0,0,,确信他看到了凯瑟琳·哈尔西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}is convinced he saw Catherine Halsey
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.79,译文,,0,0,0,,登上了一艘同样的船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}boarding a ship of the same description?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:20.25,译文,,0,0,0,,如果我跟你说有多少人说看到过凯瑟琳·哈尔西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If I told you how many Catherine Halsey sightings we have- -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.46,译文,,0,0,0,,19小时前\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Nineteen hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.46,译文,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.21,译文,,0,0,0,,她死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.55,译文,,0,0,0,,当然 他可能看错了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Of course, he could have been mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:33.14,译文,,0,0,0,,可以是任何人 与之同行的是个 原话是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It could be anyone traveling with, and I quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:35.22,译文,,0,0,0,,一个伤痕累累的男人“\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A scarred man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.60,译文,,0,0,0,,可能是他见过的最大只的人类\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Perhaps the largest human he'd ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.35,译文,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.27,译文,,0,0,0,,你一直说这话\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You keep saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:51.65,译文,,0,0,0,,你认为他还活着 还就在这个星球上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You think that he's alive, that he's here on this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:54.37,译文,,0,0,0,,我想我们很快就会知道的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I suppose we're going to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:11:05.57,注释,,0,0,0,,{\pos(184.1,217)}《光环》\N第二季 第6集\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.63,译文,,0,0,0,,暂停模拟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Pause simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.13,译文,,0,0,0,,-你在干什么  -我睡不着\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What are you doing? - I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.06,译文,,0,0,0,,你不能一直来这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you can't keep coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:42.47,译文,,0,0,0,,你不觉得有点病态了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I mean, don't you think it's a bit morbid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:45.52,译文,,0,0,0,,-我在训练  -你在惩罚自己\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm training. You're punishing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:53.57,译文,,0,0,0,,之前我们为什么不在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why weren't we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.49,译文,,0,0,0,,那些我们失去的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}AlI those people we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.12,译文,,0,0,0,,我的团队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}My team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.58,译文,,0,0,0,,都走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.58,译文,,0,0,0,,不止发生在你一个人身上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It didn't just happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:13.34,译文,,0,0,0,,没人能逃脱这种悲剧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No one escapes this kind of tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.64,译文,,0,0,0,,没有一个新兵能在护卫舰模拟中幸存\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}None of the recruits survived the Corvette simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:19.68,译文,,0,0,0,,他们会活下来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.39,译文,,0,0,0,,他们只是需要时间 需要准备\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They just need time, preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.39,译文,,0,0,0,,我得知道我们不是派他们去执行自杀任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to know we're not sending them on a suicide mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.14,译文,,0,0,0,,你曾经要求过保证吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you ever ask for a guarantee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.69,译文,,0,0,0,,他有过吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:35.40,译文,,0,0,0,,士官长走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Master Chief is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:40.32,译文,,0,0,0,,但你正在以他的形象塑造下一代\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But you are making the next generation in his image.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.24,译文,,0,0,0,,他们不是士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're not Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.95,译文,,0,0,0,,我不能把他们变成斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't make them Spartans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.50,译文,,0,0,0,,结束模拟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}End simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.04,译文,,0,0,0,,他们就是斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They are Spartans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.42,译文,,0,0,0,,你的任务就是让他们相信这点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And it's your job to make them believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.10,译文,,0,0,0,,那个能还给我了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}May I have that back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.64,译文,,0,0,0,,你想要什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is it that you want?
