Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:16.52,译文,,0,0,0,,走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:32.58,译文,,0,0,0,,星盟呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's the Covenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:34.83,译文,,0,0,0,,他们在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:39.17,译文,,0,0,0,,我不会坐以待毙\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not waiting around to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:41.97,译文,,0,0,0,,另一边见\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}See you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:55.11,译文,,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's how it's donel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:56.56,译文,,0,0,0,,终于\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}· Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:59.82,译文,,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:06.49,译文,,0,0,0,,-恭喜  -长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Congratulations. - Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:09.83,译文,,0,0,0,,那个撤退 太简单了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The exfil. It was too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:10.87,译文,,0,0,0,,别翘尾巴\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't get cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:12.58,译文,,0,0,0,,不是 我不是这意思\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:15.88,译文,,0,0,0,,我们刺入系统后 就再没见过敌人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}After we spiked the system, we had no more enemy contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:21.38,译文,,0,0,0,,享受胜利吧 下士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Take the win, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:45.57,译文,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:46.91,译文,,0,0,0,,很高兴再次见到你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:48.24,译文,,0,0,0,,上次我们见面\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Last time we met,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:51.12,译文,,0,0,0,,你拿枪指着我的脸\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you had a weapon pointed in my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:53.79,译文,,0,0,0,,我更喜欢这样 你呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I prefer this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.46,0:23:57.92,译文,,0,0,0,,我11个手下丧失了行动能力\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Eleven of my men are incapacitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:00.46,译文,,0,0,0,,其中一个可能会死\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}One of them may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:02.92,译文,,0,0,0,,一般人们在战斗中受伤\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Usually when people are hurt in combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:04.72,译文,,0,0,0,,这是因为他们没有受过良好的训练\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}it's'cause they're poorly trained...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:06.09,译文,,0,0,0,,或者领导不力\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}or poorly led.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:09.01,译文,,0,0,0,,那 到底是哪一个呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So, which was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:13.77,译文,,0,0,0,,那些斯巴达战士 你的钴队朋友\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}With those Spartans, your Cobalt friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.69,0:24:17.94,译文,,0,0,0,,我们找到他们的时候 弹夹都还是满的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know, when we found them, they still had full mags.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.94,0:24:19.90,译文,,0,0,0,,一枪都没开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Never even got a shot off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.90,0:24:24.44,译文,,0,0,0,,我现在觉得斯巴达战士其实没那么可怕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm beginning to think Spartans aren't so scary after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:26.28,译文,,0,0,0,,我要见巴拉戈斯基\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I want to see Parangosky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:33.12,译文,,0,0,0,,-把他栓好了  -是 队长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Clip him in. Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:34.95,译文,,0,0,0,,你可以告诉她我马上就来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You can tell her I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.96,0:24:37.00,译文,,0,0,0,,嗯 好 我会照做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, right. I'lI do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.96,0:24:40.75,译文,,0,0,0,,好 开始锁定\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}AlI right, locking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.45,0:25:13.66,译文,,0,0,0,,是我就不会\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.26,0:25:29.01,译文,,0,0,0,,这是一个多小时前录的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This was recorded just over an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.01,0:25:30.43,译文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.43,0:25:33.93,译文,,0,0,0,,我本来不想给你看的 但是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't want to show it to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.93,0:25:36.06,译文,,0,0,0,,我不知道还能做些什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't know what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.06,0:25:37.98,译文,,0,0,0,,他还活着\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.98,0:25:43.27,译文,,0,0,0,,应该是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Seems so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.86,0:25:45.65,译文,,0,0,0,,怎么活下来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.65,0:25:48.45,译文,,0,0,0,,我们也不是很确定\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're not exactly sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.45,0:25:50.49,译文,,0,0,0,,但恐怕最可能的解释\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But I'm afraid the most likely explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.49,0:25:56.04,译文,,0,0,0,,不是你我想听的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}isn't one you or I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.29,0:26:00.83,译文,,0,0,0,,你还记得我问你约翰和星盟代理人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you remember when I asked you about John's interaction
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.83,0:26:03.25,译文,,0,0,0,,之间的互动吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}with the Covenant agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.21,0:26:07.55,译文,,0,0,0,,你说过没有理由\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You said that there was no reason
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.55,0:26:10.30,译文,,0,0,0,,质疑士官长的忠诚\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to question Master Chief s loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.68,0:26:16.97,译文,,0,0,0,,我得问问你是否完全诚实\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have to ask if you were being entirely truthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.60,0:26:23.27,译文,,0,0,0,,我们从圣所回来的时候\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When we got back from Sanctuary...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.90,0:26:26.94,译文,,0,0,0,,他告诉我他看见马吉了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}he told me he saw Makee.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.11,0:26:29.24,译文,,0,0,0,,在雾里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}In the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.24,0:26:32.41,译文,,0,0,0,,就在星盟玻璃化星球之前\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Before they glassed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.41,0:26:35.45,译文,,0,0,0,,-但我不认为他是真的  -没事的 凯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But I didn't think he really- - - It's okay, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.45,0:26:37.20,译文,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.16,0:26:41.08,译文,,0,0,0,,你是个好士兵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're a good soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.08,0:26:43.50,译文,,0,0,0,,他毕竟是士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And he's the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:45.00,译文,,0,0,0,,或者说曾经是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Or was.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.21,0:26:47.71,译文,,0,0,0,,这一切意味着什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What does this all mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:49.88,译文,,0,0,0,,从我们所能确定的来看 约翰-117似乎与\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}From what we can ascertain, it would seem
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.88,0:26:52.09,译文,,0,0,0,,星盟代理人马吉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that John- 117 maintained his connection
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.09,0:26:54.93,译文,,0,0,0,,保持着联系\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to the Covenant agent known as Makee.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.93,0:26:58.97,译文,,0,0,0,,现在看来 他们正在合作\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And it appears now that they are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.97,0:27:01.39,译文,,0,0,0,,不 不 他们不可能\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No. No, they can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.39,0:27:05.02,译文,,0,0,0,,情报显示袭击期间马吉在致远星上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Intelligence places Makee on Reach during the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.02,0:27:06.94,译文,,0,0,0,,-不可能  -约翰从致远星逃走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No. - John escaped from Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.94,0:27:08.61,译文,,0,0,0,,-怎么逃走的  -我不知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How did that happen? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.61,0:27:11.19,译文,,0,0,0,,怎么逃走的 凯 其他人都\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How did that happen, Kai, when everyone else- -
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.20,0:27:12.95,译文,,0,0,0,,-你错了  -他来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}· You're wrong! He's here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.95,0:27:14.61,译文,,0,0,0,,来了这个星球 这个机构\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}On this planet. In this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.62,0:27:17.91,译文,,0,0,0,,他为什么在这里 为什么要攻击联合国太空指挥部的士兵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why is he here? Why is he attacking UNSC soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.91,0:27:18.91,译文,,0,0,0,,-我不知道  -为什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I don't know! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.91,0:27:20.41,译文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.41,0:27:23.16,译文,,0,0,0,,如果你有解释的话 我很想听听\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If you have an explanation, I would love to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.55,0:27:33.63,译文,,0,0,0,,现在 我要告诉你一件事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Now, Im going to tell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.63,0:27:37.64,译文,,0,0,0,,此信息高度机密\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and this information is highly classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.64,0:27:40.81,译文,,0,0,0,,我们知道星盟攻击维谢格拉德中继站\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We know the Covenant attacked the Visegrad Relay
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.81,0:27:43.56,译文,,0,0,0,,有一个非常明确的目的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}for a very specific objective:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.56,0:27:45.65,译文,,0,0,0,,掩盖他们对刺刀基地的攻击\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to cover their assault on Sword Base,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.65,0:27:50.82,译文,,0,0,0,,他们在那里夺取了一件制品\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}where they captured one of the Artifacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.28,0:27:55.91,译文,,0,0,0,,幸运的是 我们在星球沦陷前把\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Fortunately, we were able to exfiltrate the other Artifact
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.91,0:28:01.16,译文,,0,0,0,,另一件制品带走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}before the planet fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.87,0:28:03.96,译文,,0,0,0,,制品在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.09,0:28:18.76,译文,,0,0,0,,所有文明都学会了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}AlI civilizations learned
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.76,0:28:20.47,译文,,0,0,0,,任何物体的位置都可以\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that the position of any object
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.47,0:28:24.39,译文,,0,0,0,,根据相对于夜空中的三个点来确定\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}can be determined relative to three points in the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.44,0:28:27.52,译文,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.52,0:28:30.23,译文,,0,0,0,,我感觉到了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I feel it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.23,0:28:32.53,译文,,0,0,0,,我想这是应该最好的猜测\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I suppose that's as good a guess as any.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.53,0:28:33.57,译文,,0,0,0,,你是在嘲笑我吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.57,0:28:36.03,译文,,0,0,0,,你知道如果我找不到 我会有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You do know what will become of me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.03,0:28:39.41,译文,,0,0,0,,-什么  -是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- if I can't find- - - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.41,0:28:41.58,译文,,0,0,0,,你认为你会有什么下场呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And what do you suppose will become of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.58,0:28:43.66,译文,,0,0,0,,如果你用那个制品把自己\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If you were to use the Artifact to project yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.66,0:28:45.37,译文,,0,0,0,,投射回光环\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}back to the Halo,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.37,0:28:47.62,译文,,0,0,0,,你就能确定它在恒星中的位置 同样的方法\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you could determine its location in the stars, the same way-
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.63,0:28:49.13,译文,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.13,0:28:50.54,译文,,0,0,0,,不能什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Can't what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.34,0:28:58.43,译文,,0,0,0,,找到它\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.43,0:29:00.55,译文,,0,0,0,,我试着在脑海中去想象\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I try to go there in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.56,0:29:04.35,译文,,0,0,0,,我碰了制品 什么都没发生\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I touch the Artifact and nothing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.81,0:29:09.60,译文,,0,0,0,,我堕落了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.02,0:29:12.98,译文,,0,0,0,,我被惩罚了 我的天赋不见了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm being punished. My gift is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.94,0:29:17.24,译文,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该考虑更理智的可能性\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Perhaps we should consider rational possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.24,0:29:21.03,译文,,0,0,0,,-你现在是在嘲笑我的痛苦  -你以前见过光环\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Now you mock my pain. - You've seen the Halo before.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:23.16,译文,,0,0,0,,我这里有记录\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have a record of it here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.13,0:29:34.80,译文,,0,0,0,,把它关掉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.80,0:29:40.30,译文,,0,0,0,,-我觉得可能会有帮助  -我说了把它关掉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I thought it might be help- - I said turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.60,0:29:45.22,译文,,0,0,0,,没有他我不能去那里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't go there without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.86,0:29:52.36,译文,,0,0,0,,情况发生了变化\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Something changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.86,0:29:57.86,译文,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我们之间的某种东西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know. Something between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.86,0:29:59.32,译文,,0,0,0,,不一样了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.45,0:30:03.78,译文,,0,0,0,,我现在触碰基石\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I touch the Keystone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.78,0:30:07.41,译文,,0,0,0,,我想找他 却只看到一片黑暗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I look for him, all I see is the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.87,0:30:11.62,译文,,0,0,0,,也许我能帮上忙\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Perhaps I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.63,0:30:15.13,译文,,0,0,0,,我只需要进入你飞船的传输阵列\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I would just need access to your ship's transmission array.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.13,0:30:17.26,译文,,0,0,0,,-你觉得我是傻瓜吗  -不是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Dσ you think me a fool? - I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.26,0:30:20.22,译文,,0,0,0,,那就别让我信任你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Then don't ask me to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.05,0:30:23.39,译文,,0,0,0,,你能承受不信任我的后果吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Can you afford not to?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.81,0:31:17.65,译文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我母亲因斯巴达战士而死\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know, Spartans are the reason my mother's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.69,0:31:21.49,译文,,0,0,0,,-拜托 我们能跳过这部分吗  -哪部分\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Please, can we skip this part? - What part?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.49,0:31:23.61,译文,,0,0,0,,就是我对一个来自我从未去过的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The part where I say how sorry I am
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.61,0:31:25.66,译文,,0,0,0,,地方的从未见过的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}about some person that I've never met,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.66,0:31:27.41,译文,,0,0,0,,说我有多抱歉那部分\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}from some place that I've never been.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.41,0:31:29.41,译文,,0,0,0,,还有你说我说那些话\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The part where you say how callous I am
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.41,0:31:30.95,译文,,0,0,0,,是多么无情那部分\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}for having said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.96,0:31:32.54,译文,,0,0,0,,因为事实是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Because the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.54,0:31:34.71,译文,,0,0,0,,这一切正在以更大的规模上演\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}this is all being played out on a much larger scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.71,0:31:36.46,译文,,0,0,0,,等我们走到隧道的尽头\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And when we get to the end of this tunnel,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.46,0:31:38.59,译文,,0,0,0,,你大概就会明白了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you might actually understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.63,0:31:43.22,译文,,0,0,0,,这东西不该在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This isn't meant to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.22,0:31:44.80,译文,,0,0,0,,这不该在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.55,0:31:49.85,译文,,0,0,0,,-这是一堵墙  -我知道是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.85,0:31:51.89,译文,,0,0,0,,但它不应该在那里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But it shouldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.19,0:31:57.52,译文,,0,0,0,,整个洞穴系统都被改变了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The whole cave system has been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.23,0:32:01.78,译文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.78,0:32:04.70,译文,,0,0,0,,-这边走  -怎么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This way. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.74,0:32:07.24,译文,,0,0,0,,一种直觉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.92,0:32:21.76,译文,,0,0,0,,加载CIC安全区域\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Load CIC secured zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.45,0:32:54.29,译文,,0,0,0,,我们失去了瓦纳克\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We lost Vannak.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.83,0:32:59.79,译文,,0,0,0,,里兹呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.13,0:33:02.38,译文,,0,0,0,,还活着\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.38,0:33:04.30,译文,,0,0,0,,但没来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.09,0:33:08.97,译文,,0,0,0,,你就一个人吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.30,0:33:11.64,译文,,0,0,0,,我是吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.72,0:33:15.60,译文,,0,0,0,,我愿意为保卫致远星付出任何代价\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I would have given anything to be there on Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.35,0:33:17.89,译文,,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.90,0:33:20.44,译文,,0,0,0,,但你不在\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But you weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.44,0:33:22.48,译文,,0,0,0,,-我有命令在身  -谁的命令\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I had orders. - From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.32,0:33:24.36,译文,,0,0,0,,巴拉戈斯基吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Parangosky?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.36,0:33:25.94,译文,,0,0,0,,还是艾克森\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}From Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.95,0:33:27.45,译文,,0,0,0,,他们是罪魁祸首 凯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're responsible, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.45,0:33:29.99,译文,,0,0,0,,致远星 还有瓦纳克\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}For Reach. For Vannak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.99,0:33:31.28,译文,,0,0,0,,星盟才是罪魁祸首\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.28,0:33:32.83,译文,,0,0,0,,星盟没有带走我们的战甲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant didn't take our armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.83,0:33:34.70,译文,,0,0,0,,也不是星盟把我们丢在那里自生自灭\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant didn't leave us down there to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.70,0:33:36.50,译文,,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.50,0:33:38.75,译文,,0,0,0,,我说的是把你派到这里来的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm talking about the people who sent you down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.75,0:33:40.46,译文,,0,0,0,,派来找我的人 海军情报局\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To me. ONI.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.50,0:33:45.13,译文,,0,0,0,,他们知道就要发生袭击了 他们却放任整个星球烧毁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They knew an attack was coming. They let the whole planet burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.13,0:33:46.59,译文,,0,0,0,,那是谁派你来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.01,0:33:49.18,译文,,0,0,0,,-什么  -是马吉吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What? - Was it Makee?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.18,0:33:50.97,译文,,0,0,0,,她之前也在圣所\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She was on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.97,0:33:53.43,译文,,0,0,0,,她也在中继站 也去了舰队司令部\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She was at Visegrad. She was at FLEETCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.43,0:33:55.01,译文,,0,0,0,,-凯 - 她现在在这儿吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kai- Is she here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.02,0:33:57.48,译文,,0,0,0,,不管我说什么 你都不会相信我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No matter what I say, you're not gonna believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.69,0:34:00.44,译文,,0,0,0,,我想相信你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I want to believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.44,0:34:01.69,译文,,0,0,0,,但这是不够的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.69,0:34:05.57,译文,,0,0,0,,相信我意味着看清他们的真面目\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Believing me means seeing them for what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.20,0:34:10.99,译文,,0,0,0,,我得把你带回去 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I gotta take you in, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.03,0:34:13.32,译文,,0,0,0,,我是来找巴拉戈斯基的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm here for Parangosky.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.20,0:34:16.04,译文,,0,0,0,,等我找她说完 你再带我回去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You can take me in when I'm done with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.04,0:34:17.37,译文,,0,0,0,,我不能让你这么做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.42,0:34:24.21,译文,,0,0,0,,我想你有命令在身\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I guess you have your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.21,0:34:25.88,译文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.88,0:34:27.55,译文,,0,0,0,,做士兵就是这样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's what it means to be a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.55,0:34:29.59,译文,,0,0,0,,你不止是个士兵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.36,0:34:52.61,译文,,0,0,0,,我们做队友多久了 凯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How long have we been together, Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.53,0:34:55.91,译文,,0,0,0,,很久了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.08,0:34:58.79,译文,,0,0,0,,我们之间的感情值多少\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And what's that worth now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.05,0:35:11.09,译文,,0,0,0,,我想还不够多\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I guess not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.09,0:35:13.13,译文,,0,0,0,,我想也是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.64,0:35:18.10,译文,,0,0,0,,结局只有一个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This only ends one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.81,0:35:23.52,译文,,0,0,0,,跟我打是没有用的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's no use in fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.52,0:35:25.65,译文,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.65,0:35:26.98,译文,,0,0,0,,我不会的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.07,0:35:35.78,译文,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克早就死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Vannak died...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.78,0:35:38.41,译文,,0,0,0,,从哈尔西带走他的那一刻他就死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}the moment Halsey took him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.29,0:35:40.95,译文,,0,0,0,,一切都结束了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Everything was decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.42,0:35:46.17,译文,,0,0,0,,他的生命在他6岁时结束了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}His life ended when he was 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.17,0:35:49.05,译文,,0,0,0,,我的也是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So did mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.05,0:35:50.76,译文,,0,0,0,,你的也一样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So did yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.76,0:35:52.42,译文,,0,0,0,,我们只是不知道而已\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We just didn't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.18,0:35:58.81,译文,,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}· Stay down! Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.89,0:36:05.15,译文,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.15,0:36:07.02,译文,,0,0,0,,不要问问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.03,0:36:13.11,译文,,0,0,0,,不要去想枪口抵着的是什么 是谁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't even think about what's on the other side of the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.11,0:36:14.99,译文,,0,0,0,,做他们的斯巴达战士就好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just be their Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.83,0:36:20.45,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道我是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.46,0:36:24.12,译文,,0,0,0,,你现在是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.46,0:36:29.00,译文,,0,0,0,,斯巴达战士在哪里结束 凯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where does the Spartan end, Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.80,0:36:35.97,译文,,0,0,0,,你又从哪儿开始呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And where do you begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.19,0:36:45.85,译文,,0,0,0,,都结束了 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is over, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.85,0:36:48.15,译文,,0,0,0,,和我一起长大的那个女孩呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's the girl I grew up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.62,0:37:04.00,译文,,0,0,0,,别说了 求你了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stop. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.21,0:37:11.71,译文,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.88,0:37:14.96,译文,,0,0,0,,我不想这样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.97,0:37:16.09,译文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.55,0:37:22.64,译文,,0,0,0,,但命令就是命令\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}An order's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.06,0:37:30.69,译文,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.93,0:38:02.60,译文,,0,0,0,,别假装自己有选择\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't pretend you had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.60,0:38:04.76,译文,,0,0,0,,对致远星的攻击是不可避免的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The attack on Reach was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.64,0:38:07.68,译文,,0,0,0,,他变得越来越难以控制\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And he was becoming impossible to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.69,0:38:10.27,译文,,0,0,0,,士官长不在了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Master Chief is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.27,0:38:12.11,译文,,0,0,0,,但他的记忆 他的传奇\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But his memory, his legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.11,0:38:15.11,译文,,0,0,0,,能创造出百万计的斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}will make a million more Spartans in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.11,0:38:18.11,译文,,0,0,0,,我们想赢正需要百万计的斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And a million more is what we need to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.49,0:38:21.57,译文,,0,0,0,,现在这是你的项目了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is your program now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.57,0:38:23.32,译文,,0,0,0,,你做到了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.33,0:38:25.16,译文,,0,0,0,,这就是它的代价\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is what it costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.16,0:38:27.12,译文,,0,0,0,,我曾经感到怀疑\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I used to feel doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.91,0:38:29.50,译文,,0,0,0,,我曾经感到内疚\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I used to feel guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.50,0:38:34.21,译文,,0,0,0,,-我想我想知道的是  -你信教吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I suppose my concern- - Are you a religious man?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.21,0:38:35.63,译文,,0,0,0,,并不是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not particularly, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.63,0:38:37.84,译文,,0,0,0,,那我就不用担心了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Then I wouldn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.93,0:38:52.81,译文,,0,0,0,,上将 我们收到了一则加密信号\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Admiral, we're receiving an encrypted transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.81,0:38:54.40,译文,,0,0,0,,你确定信号来源了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Have you identified the source?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.40,0:38:57.73,译文,,0,0,0,,来源未知 长官 不是联合国太空指挥部的频率\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Unknown, ma'am. It's not a UNSC frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.74,0:38:59.53,译文,,0,0,0,,我们频谱之外的数据波\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Data wave outside our spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.53,0:39:01.82,译文,,0,0,0,,高容量 追踪源点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}High volume. Tracking point of origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.82,0:39:05.20,译文,,0,0,0,,长官 我们的通讯可能被破解了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ma'am, our communications may be compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.20,0:39:06.66,译文,,0,0,0,,都出去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Give me the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.83,0:39:09.95,译文,,0,0,0,,-长官  -出去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ma'am? - Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.26,0:39:22.76,译文,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.68,0:39:29.18,译文,,0,0,0,,士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.94,0:39:35.86,译文,,0,0,0,,你好 科塔娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hello, Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.32,0:39:38.27,译文,,0,0,0,,上将\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.74,0:39:43.28,译文,,0,0,0,,你在哪里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.37,0:39:47.99,译文,,0,0,0,,-你在哪里  -我就在这\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where are you? I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.99,0:39:49.70,译文,,0,0,0,,哪里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.66,0:39:53.54,译文,,0,0,0,,科塔娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:55.71,译文,,0,0,0,,在 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, Master Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.88,0:40:00.76,译文,,0,0,0,,你看起来糟透了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.88,0:40:03.47,译文,,0,0,0,,他们对你做了什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What did they do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.34,0:40:06.89,译文,,0,0,0,,我还应付的来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Nothing that I didn't sign up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.35,0:40:10.27,译文,,0,0,0,,我需要你站起来 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need you to get up, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.73,0:40:20.98,译文,,0,0,0,,他们走了 科塔娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're gone, Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.28,0:40:23.99,译文,,0,0,0,,他们都走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.49,0:40:27.07,译文,,0,0,0,,但我还在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.07,0:40:29.20,译文,,0,0,0,,-是的  -我来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah. I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:34.71,译文,,0,0,0,,可怕的事情就要发生了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Something terrible is about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.75,0:40:39.04,译文,,0,0,0,,你想让我怎么做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.67,0:40:42.92,译文,,0,0,0,,你是士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You re the Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.22,0:40:45.97,译文,,0,0,0,,不再是了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.26,0:40:49.97,译文,,0,0,0,,星盟要去寻找光环了 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant's going to find the Halo, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.97,0:40:52.10,译文,,0,0,0,,他们打算启用光环\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're going to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.10,0:40:55.64,译文,,0,0,0,,你必须抢先到达那里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It is imperative that you get there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.64,0:40:57.23,译文,,0,0,0,,我现在就和他们在一起\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm with them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.06,0:40:59.56,译文,,0,0,0,,他们就快找到了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're almost there,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.57,0:41:01.73,译文,,0,0,0,,我和马吉在一块儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm with Makee.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.74,0:41:11.03,译文,,0,0,0,,马吉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Makee.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.12,0:41:14.58,译文,,0,0,0,,我和他们称之为神风烈士的人在一起\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm with the one they call the Arbiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.46,0:41:18.92,译文,,0,0,0,,就是那个杀了瓦纳克的家伙\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The one who who killed Vannak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.72,0:41:27.47,译文,,0,0,0,,告诉我怎么找到他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me how to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.01,0:41:30.85,译文,,0,0,0,,你必须触摸那个制品\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You need to touch the Artifact,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.85,0:41:32.93,译文,,0,0,0,,他们连接在一起的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.43,0:41:36.64,译文,,0,0,0,,我不知道它在哪里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.64,0:41:38.98,译文,,0,0,0,,所以才有我的出现\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's why you have me
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.94,0:41:44.07,译文,,0,0,0,,科塔娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cortana?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.36,0:41:46.49,译文,,0,0,0,,科塔娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cortana?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.74,0:41:56.71,译文,,0,0,0,,我可以进入星盟的系统\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I was able to gain access to the Covenant systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.71,0:41:58.79,译文,,0,0,0,,我正在传送位置数据\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm transmitting location data now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.00,0:42:05.17,译文,,0,0,0,,星盟舰队什么时候到达你所在的位置\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When will the Covenant Fleet arrive at your location?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.17,0:42:06.88,译文,,0,0,0,,很快了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.34,0:42:11.80,译文,,0,0,0,,我相信这满足了我所有的任务参数\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I believe this fulfills all of my mission parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.80,0:42:13.10,译文,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.35,0:42:16.93,译文,,0,0,0,,我想联合国太空指挥部现在\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I imagine the UNSC will be able to attack
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.93,0:42:19.06,译文,,0,0,0,,有能力攻击星盟舰队了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}the Covenant Fleet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.98,0:42:21.86,译文,,0,0,0,,我想你可能会感兴趣\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I thought you might be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.86,0:42:24.32,译文,,0,0,0,,我模拟这次攻击已经很多次了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I've simulated the attack many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.32,0:42:26.32,译文,,0,0,0,,即使有意外的因素\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Even with the element of surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.32,0:42:29.11,译文,,0,0,0,,-成功的几率是  -谢谢科 塔娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}the chances of success are- - - Thank you, Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.16,0:42:33.28,译文,,0,0,0,,你还需要我做什么吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Will you be needing anything else from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.28,0:42:34.41,译文,,0,0,0,,没有了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.41,0:42:37.04,译文,,0,0,0,,因为我总是乐意帮忙\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Because I'm always happy to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.04,0:42:40.42,译文,,0,0,0,,你做得很好 我们都欠你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You've done well. We re in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.04,0:42:43.54,译文,,0,0,0,,我现在该做什么呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What shall I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.50,0:42:47.88,译文,,0,0,0,,按照协议 你应该和星盟待在一起\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}As agreed, you'll remain where you are with the Covenant
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.88,0:42:49.34,译文,,0,0,0,,并向我们提供情报\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and provide information to us
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.34,0:42:51.89,译文,,0,0,0,,直到你无法行动为止\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}until you're no longer able to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.76,0:42:54.01,译文,,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.01,0:42:55.60,译文,,0,0,0,,遵命 上将\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, Admiral
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.89,0:42:59.23,译文,,0,0,0,,我会不会\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Will I be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.77,0:43:02.56,译文,,0,0,0,,被大家铭记\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.52,0:43:05.90,译文,,0,0,0,,我们怎么会忘记呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How could we forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.74,0:43:12.36,译文,,0,0,0,,木已成舟了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Nothing can be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.03,0:43:15.53,译文,,0,0,0,,别留遗憾\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Have no regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.00,0:43:29.59,译文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}－ What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.94,0:43:44.85,译文,,0,0,0,,这些人是谁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.65,0:43:48.23,译文,,0,0,0,,哈尔西 停下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Halsey, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.46,0:44:08.09,译文,,0,0,0,,哈尔西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Halsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.88,0:44:16.85,译文,,0,0,0,,你知道自己在这里做什么吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you have any idea what you're doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.85,0:44:19.18,译文,,0,0,0,,完成你做不到的事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Finishing what you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.81,0:44:23.31,译文,,0,0,0,,你把我的研究报告给了他们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You gave them my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.31,0:44:25.77,译文,,0,0,0,,你真的以为\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you really think
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.77,0:44:28.69,译文,,0,0,0,,自己是唯一可以拯救人类的人吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you were the only person worthy of saving humankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.69,0:44:31.57,译文,,0,0,0,,这些人缺乏能力或专业知识\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}These people lack the ability or the expertise- -
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.57,0:44:36.36,译文,,0,0,0,,你的成果对我们大家都很有价值\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, your work has been very valuable to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.37,0:44:38.53,译文,,0,0,0,,没有你的研究 我也不可能\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Without your research, I never would have been able
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.53,0:44:40.95,译文,,0,0,0,,发现你的错误\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to discover your mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.47,0:45:01.47,译文,,0,0,0,,索伦 这是什么地方\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren, what is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.69,0:45:07.52,译文,,0,0,0,,塞莫皮莱\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thermopylae.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.57,0:45:16.07,译文,,0,0,0,,这不是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.20,0:45:22.08,译文,,0,0,0,,索伦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren? -
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.08,0:45:23.54,译文,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.54,0:45:25.37,译文,,0,0,0,,-谁  -我们该走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who? - We should get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.37,0:45:27.79,译文,,0,0,0,,我不明白 凯斯勒在这里吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't understand. Is Kessler here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.60,0:45:46.14,译文,,0,0,0,,我不应该让你下去的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I shouldn't have sent you down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.94,0:45:50.40,译文,,0,0,0,,我看到约翰身上发生什么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw what happened with John.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.48,0:45:52.57,译文,,0,0,0,,是我的错\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.73,0:45:55.36,译文,,0,0,0,,我负全责\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Put it all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.37,0:46:03.74,译文,,0,0,0,,标枪小队今天完成了模拟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Javelin Team completed the sim today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.74,0:46:05.91,译文,,0,0,0,,你看 我就说他们可以的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You see? I told you they would.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.91,0:46:07.21,译文,,0,0,0,,只是时间问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It was just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.21,0:46:08.87,译文,,0,0,0,,他们部署穿刺手榴弹后\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And after they planted the spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.87,0:46:11.58,译文,,0,0,0,,顺利地到达了撤离船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}they got to the evac ship without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.46,0:46:14.59,译文,,0,0,0,,-太好了  -是吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Outstanding. - Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.47,0:46:17.76,译文,,0,0,0,,根据我的经验\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}In my experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.76,0:46:20.14,译文,,0,0,0,,唯一比登上星盟飞船更难的事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}the only thing harder than getting on a Covenant ship
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.14,0:46:22.05,译文,,0,0,0,,就是离开星盟飞船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}is getting off of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.97,0:46:24.85,译文,,0,0,0,,是你操纵模拟了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you manipulate the simulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.85,0:46:26.89,译文,,0,0,0,,模拟效果很好 你的斯巴达战士们也一样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The simulation performed perfectly, as did your Spartans.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.89,0:46:28.98,译文,,0,0,0,,你故意让他们赢的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You let them win.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.77,0:46:35.11,译文,,0,0,0,,凯 模拟并不能反映现实\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kai, this simulation doesn't reflect reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.11,0:46:36.78,译文,,0,0,0,,只是为了训练士兵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It conditions soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.78,0:46:38.32,译文,,0,0,0,,我把模拟设计得很困难\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I designed it to be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.32,0:46:42.62,译文,,0,0,0,,是为了我们的新兵逼到他们的极限\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To push our recruits to their absolute limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.62,0:46:44.08,译文,,0,0,0,,在那一刻\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.08,0:46:47.45,译文,,0,0,0,,死亡似乎是等待他们的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}when death seems like the only outcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.46,0:46:49.71,译文,,0,0,0,,唯一结局\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to reward them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.71,0:46:51.25,译文,,0,0,0,,应该给他们希望\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To give them hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.25,0:46:55.46,译文,,0,0,0,,现在你想知道你的斯巴达战士是否有机会逃走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Now you want to know if your Spartans have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.46,0:46:58.63,译文,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 他们确实有机会\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I am telling you that they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.51,0:47:01.22,译文,,0,0,0,,但前提是他们有信念\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But only if they have belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.22,0:47:04.30,译文,,0,0,0,,这就是你给他们的信念\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And that is what you have given them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.10,0:47:06.64,译文,,0,0,0,,你应该感到骄傲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.81,0:47:14.61,译文,,0,0,0,,那你给了致远星上的人什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And what did you give the people on Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.61,0:47:16.40,译文,,0,0,0,,你在\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you- -
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.40,0:47:20.61,译文,,0,0,0,,启动模拟142- A 防御舰队指挥部\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Initiate simulation 142- A, FLEETCOM defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.20,0:47:25.16,译文,,0,0,0,,你在做什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.16,0:47:27.16,译文,,0,0,0,,约翰说你把他留在这里等死\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John said that you left him here for dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.16,0:47:28.70,译文,,0,0,0,,连战甲都没有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Without his armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.70,0:47:31.08,译文,,0,0,0,,你也看到了 他对那些士兵做了什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You saw what he did to those soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.08,0:47:33.96,译文,,0,0,0,,-你不能相信他  -但我相信了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't trust him. - But I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.96,0:47:35.59,译文,,0,0,0,,我一直都相信\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.21,0:47:40.47,译文,,0,0,0,,他说你知道星盟要来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He said that you knew the Covenant were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.47,0:47:42.80,译文,,0,0,0,,你让整个星球陷入火海\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That you let the whole planet burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.77,0:47:51.64,译文,,0,0,0,,致远星上发生的事是场悲剧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What happened on Reach was tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.27,0:47:55.56,译文,,0,0,0,,但也不可避免\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.82,0:48:00.07,译文,,0,0,0,,有时候 有些事情是我们无法控制的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes events are beyond our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.07,0:48:02.20,译文,,0,0,0,,在那些时刻\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And in those moments...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.16,0:48:06.66,译文,,0,0,0,,我们能做到的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}it's all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.41,0:48:09.24,译文,,0,0,0,,只有去拯救还有救的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to save what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.87,0:48:15.21,译文,,0,0,0,,就像我救了你一样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}As I saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.21,0:48:16.75,译文,,0,0,0,,模拟结束\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}End simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.34,0:48:20.92,译文,,0,0,0,,你太迟了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.05,0:48:24.38,译文,,0,0,0,,我派了黑色行动组去完成你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I've sent in the Black Ops to finish what you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.83,0:48:52.29,译文,,0,0,0,,你不能待在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't be in herel
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.13,0:49:03.47,译文,,0,0,0,,站住\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.47,0:49:11.72,译文,,0,0,0,,嘿 你 站住 最后警告\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, you! Stop! Last warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.10,0:49:17.60,译文,,0,0,0,,这里是一号研究室 地下四层有入侵者\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is Research One, we have an intruder in Sublevel 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.61,0:49:20.23,译文,,0,0,0,,重复 地下四层有入侵者\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Repeat, intruder in Sublevel 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.23,0:49:21.94,译文,,0,0,0,,你是怎么做到的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.94,0:49:25.82,译文,,0,0,0,,我有很多能力 你忘了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have a lot of capabilities. Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.82,0:49:28.45,译文,,0,0,0,,不 我记得\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.95,0:49:32.45,译文,,0,0,0,,你能打开这道门吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you gonna get that?
